<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Tax Organizer Assistance</title>
  </head>
  <body
    style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; padding: 20px;"
  >
    <table
      style="max-width:600px; width:100%; margin:auto; border-collapse: collapse;"
    >
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">
          <h2 style="color: #2a7ae2;">Hi {{name}},</h2>
          <p>If you’re unsure how to complete your tax organizer or what
            documents to include, don’t worry. We’re here to answer your
            questions, help review what you have, and guide you through anything
            you’re missing.</p>
          <p>We're currently working with thousands of clients. If you want your
            return filed on time, we need to begin gathering your information
            immediately. Waiting too long could slow down the process and push
            you further back in the queue.</p>
          <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-weight: bold;">Call us at
            <a
              href="tel:{{number}}"
              style="color: #2a7ae2; text-decoration: none;"
            >{{number}}</a>
            and we’ll help you move forward.</p>
          <div style="margin-top: 40px;">
            {{{signature}}}
          </div>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>